snippet.title: Minecraft World of Color Update trailer
snippet.description: To celebrate the release of the 1.12 update for PC and Mac, we asked the Reddit community to share their most colorful builds. And they did! Read more about the update here: https://minecraft.net/en-us/article/world-color-released
